High Consumption Professionals: Individuals with high educational backgrounds engaged in high-paying professions with high consumption habits.
Median Consumption Investors: Professionals with median education and consumption levels primarily in investment roles.
Slightly Low to Low Consumption Workers: Workers with lower educational backgrounds or lower paying jobs characterized by slightly low to low consumption.
Slightly High Consumption IT Engineers: IT engineers with slightly high consumption habits, generally holding higher degrees.
Low Education and Consumption Individual: Individuals with lower education levels exhibiting lower consumption patterns.
